<bibRefCitation author="Pitts, J. P. &amp; Parker, F. D. &amp; Pitts-Singer, T. L." box="[1233,1431,908,932]" etAl="et al." firstAuthor="Pitts" journalOrPublisher="Journal of the Kansas Entomological Society" pageId="24" pageNumber="25" pagination="223 - 234" part="77" refId="ref58601" refString="Pitts, J. P., Parker, F. D. &amp; Pitts-Singer, T. L. (2004) A review of the Sphaeropthalma uro species-group (Hymenoptera: Mutillidae), with taxonomic changes. Journal of the Kansas Entomological Society, 77, 223 - 234." title="A review of the Sphaeropthalma uro species-group (Hymenoptera: Mutillidae), with taxonomic changes" type="journal article" year="2004">
